WEBVTT

00:03.160 --> 00:03.840
Your son

00:05.000 --> 00:05.760
Understands

00:07.960 --> 00:08.720
Good

00:10.760 --> 00:12.960
This Chu Huan is a loyal and righteous man

00:13.440 --> 00:14.480
Before he goes

00:15.440 --> 00:16.720
Go see him

00:19.400 --> 00:19.880
Yes

00:36.240 --> 00:36.880
Your Highness

00:37.680 --> 00:38.280
You've come

00:54.720 --> 00:55.880
Before acting

00:57.280 --> 00:59.000
Your subject thought he might lose his head

01:00.080 --> 01:01.080
Just didn't think

01:01.600 --> 01:03.680
It would nearly drag Your Highness down

01:06.680 --> 01:07.320
Chu Huan

01:07.960 --> 01:09.040
The order was mine

01:10.200 --> 01:11.480
You've followed me since the north

01:12.520 --> 01:12.800
I

01:16.200 --> 01:17.880
Your subject first followed Your Highness

01:18.440 --> 01:19.960
Only for the prince's salary

01:20.280 --> 01:21.560
Following Your Highness south

01:22.560 --> 01:24.120
Was to preserve life and body

01:25.600 --> 01:26.640
Now your subject

01:27.440 --> 01:29.000
Is guilty before heaven's might

01:29.520 --> 01:30.960
Guilty before the times

01:32.080 --> 01:33.440
Why does Your Highness blame yourself?

01:36.680 --> 01:37.960
The high noble families

01:38.640 --> 01:40.960
Are the mountains connecting all of Jiangnan

01:42.000 --> 01:44.040
Both protecting the current Xuan Kingdom

01:45.320 --> 01:46.680
And keeping the Son of Heaven

01:47.360 --> 01:49.240
From leaving their shadow

01:50.280 --> 01:51.040
Your subject

01:52.000 --> 01:52.880
Since I cannot be

01:52.880 --> 01:54.000
The blade that splits mountains

01:56.440 --> 01:57.680
Then to be Your Highness's

01:58.320 --> 01:59.320
Stepping stone

01:59.680 --> 02:00.520
Is fine

02:03.280 --> 02:04.480
When we went south

02:05.000 --> 02:06.480
Your subject had family and old friends

02:06.640 --> 02:07.680
Left in the north

02:08.600 --> 02:09.440
Under your subject

02:09.760 --> 02:10.760
Are many people

02:10.760 --> 02:11.720
Like your subject

02:16.480 --> 02:17.800
Your Highness once promised me

02:18.800 --> 02:19.680
Them

02:20.960 --> 02:23.240
And the millions of northern people

02:24.680 --> 02:25.840
That one day

02:26.600 --> 02:27.880
We would defeat the Wutu in the north

02:28.760 --> 02:30.040
And recover our land

02:32.960 --> 02:33.960
Is there anything else

02:35.880 --> 02:37.280
You need me to do?

02:38.600 --> 02:40.360
Your subject has a capable student

02:40.840 --> 02:42.080
Named Zhu Yuanzhi

02:44.520 --> 02:45.800
Please, Your Highness

02:46.600 --> 02:47.320
Put him to good use

02:50.760 --> 02:51.480
Certainly

02:57.640 --> 02:58.560
This half journey

02:59.240 --> 03:00.280
To be able to serve Your Highness

03:00.840 --> 03:01.880
Shelter from wind and rain

03:02.560 --> 03:03.680
And block blades

03:04.480 --> 03:05.680
Is Huan's fortune

03:12.880 --> 03:14.080
This cup of wine

03:14.600 --> 03:15.480
Your subject

03:16.160 --> 03:16.960
Deserves

03:20.600 --> 03:21.640
To Your Highness
